1 What is this?
═══════════════

  This is my ~/bin directory, full of scripts and stuff that might be
  handy for someone.


2 Why is this?
══════════════

  I don't want to lose it.


3 How do I use this?
════════════════════

  Download the scripts you want to use, or just clone the entire
  repo. Then add the scripts to your PATH environment variable.
